cs.SD, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.SD, cs.AI 

This paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of cs.SD (Sound) as it deals with voice conversion and improving speech quality. It could also belong to cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it involves natural language processing and speech synthesis. Additionally, it involves machine learning techniques, which could place it in the sub-categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, it could also be categorized under cs.CV (Computer Vision) as it involves image-to-image translation techniques.
